Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.39,0:00:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春天到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.26,0:00:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 居然在那里使出Homing Jump
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.26,0:00:18.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.16,0:00:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟…竟然大胆地发动突击
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.83,0:00:21.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好快
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.03,0:00:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是平常的3倍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.07,0:00:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没那么快吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.17,0:00:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明都已经是春天了 你们就没别的事好做吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.08,0:00:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问这个问题的我是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.58,0:00:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个模式你预测不到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.31,0:00:36.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.12,0:00:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.49,0:00:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是"蓝尔"所以选"扎古"是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.63,0:00:48.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.79,0:00:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终…终于连大野也沦陷了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.03,0:00:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是春天所以选扎古？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.42,0:02:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,266)} 量产型制造过程的比较研究
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.36,0:02:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为春天到了 所以我想差不多也该开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.13,0:02:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我将HGUC都买齐了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.13,0:02:35.03,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HGUC（High Grade Universal Century）系列 Bandai于1999年推出的HG系列模型的一个分支系列\N只包含了U.C.纪元中出现的各种MS、MA等，有价格低廉、组合方便的优点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.10,0:02:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在你才要开始玩这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.14,0:02:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,零件好多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.41,0:02:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不选B3而选B型 是因为对蓝尔的爱吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.18,0:02:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.01,0:02:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笹…笹原选的是吉姆？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.35,0:02:52.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般很少有人会从那个玩起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.88,0:02:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢量产机的无机质感
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.02,0:02:57.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就应该选扎古吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.99,0:03:00.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是扎古太出风头了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.66,0:03:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不喜欢不对称的设计
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.83,0:03:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那CANNON也是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.23,0:03:05.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法接受
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.23,0:03:07.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就某种意义而言 你还真是条汉子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.70,0:03:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们给我用日文对话！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.27,0:03:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对塑料模型没兴趣是吗 春日部
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.24,0:03:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是塑料模型啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.98,0:03:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.08,0:03:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到MG系列
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.08,0:03:26.18,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MG（Master Grade）系列，于1995年开始推出\N面向15岁以上中高级模型制作水平人群的主力产品系列
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.25,0:03:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就属包装内的图像 最让人难以抗拒的了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.59,0:03:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好帅气哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.06,0:03:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 老实说 要摆出那种姿势得需要相当程度的改造
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.76,0:03:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就先来举办让初学者能提升技术的研习会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.40,0:03:44.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28}(初学者技术晋升讲座)\N(光这么做就差很多)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.04,0:03:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还特别印了这种东西吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.77,0:03:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实春天是最适合制作模型的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.54,0:03:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏冬季不只气温是问题
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.21,0:03:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,湿气更是难以掌控
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.45,0:03:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.51,0:03:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没在问你这些
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.08,0:03:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至于秋天为什么不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.98,0:04:02.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为在制作途中 天气可能会变冷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.42,0:04:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漆会变得很难上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.86,0:04:06.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都说我没问了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.26,0:04:08.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们就马上开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.06,0:04:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.06,0:04:15.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分得好细哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.20,0:04:16.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这些就能让你惊讶成那样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.83,0:04:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看你还是先别碰PG比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.83,0:04:19.83,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PG（Perfect Grade）系列是1999年开始以“完美GUNDAM模型”为口号\N推出的1:60系列高等级模型，面向高级模型爱好者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.90,0:04:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田中 难不成你都完成了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.44,0:04:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大致上都完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.58,0:04:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塑料模型啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.34,0:04:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是玩具吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.71,0:04:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那句话实在无法听过就算
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.98,0:04:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.05,0:04:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塑料模型跟玩具是不同的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.22,0:04:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这东西必须亲手组装
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.02,0:04:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那比玩具还不如是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.29,0:04:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说错了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.06,0:04:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓的塑料模型
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.33,0:04:48.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得经过一个个零件的组装程序
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.13,0:04:50.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能注入制作者的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.04,0:04:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它所蕴涵的意义 与玩具比起来可说是天差地别
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.94,0:04:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说 像这样的整套组件
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.88,0:04:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将忠实地呈现出制作者的个性…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.98,0:05:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.01,0:05:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你做的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.62,0:05:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我做的没错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.58,0:05:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.35,0:05:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.05,0:05:07.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦什么咦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.99,0:05:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个借我看啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.22,0:05:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.64,0:05:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还会动耶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.38,0:05:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.84,0:05:35.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要动的时候 请你从关节开始好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.61,0:05:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是先移动肩膀 再动手肘
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.22,0:05:40.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照顺序来 而不是用力的扭它
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.05,0:05:41.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.05,0:05:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.69,0:05:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么说才好 应该是为了安全起见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.93,0:05:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.50,0:05:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.24,0:06:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么要刻意把它放在那种不稳定的地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.51,0:06:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故意的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.57,0:06:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是故意的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.57,0:06:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.44,0:06:07.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想说放在高一点的地方 看起来应该会比较帅…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.01,0:06:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 毫发无伤
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.12,0:06:15.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓得我一身冷汗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.95,0:06:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,严禁烟火哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.09,0:06:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我把东西收起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.89,0:06:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.24,0:06:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可…可能说得稍微过份了一点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.17,0:06:37.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真让人感觉到文化的隔阂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.48,0:06:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那种问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.04,0:06:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后果很恐怖哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.02,0:06:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.96,0:06:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田中很喜欢塑料模型
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.69,0:06:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的田中还真是个十足的OTAKU
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.13,0:07:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要谈到自己喜欢的事 他就会侃侃而谈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.34,0:07:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不玩塑料模型吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.57,0:07:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不太玩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.44,0:07:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为技术差是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.48,0:07:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田中所说的其实只能代表制作者的逻辑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.88,0:07:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不代表全都是正确的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.39,0:07:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的说法也挺OTAKU的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.29,0:07:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战果如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.06,0:07:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.46,0:07:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.67,0:07:36.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漫研的格斗游戏大会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.87,0:07:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.27,0:07:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田中他们开始做模型了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.71,0:07:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高坂 你也会做吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.82,0:07:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.15,0:07:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MG的吉打
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.65,0:07:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来因为太难而中途放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.09,0:07:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后来还是由田中接手帮我完成的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.66,0:08:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么你不是很喜欢咯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.36,0:08:04.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算普通吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.13,0:08:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要看吉打钢卡吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.80,0:08:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.58,0:08:25.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽可能在今天之内完成假组吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.25,0:08:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.42,0:08:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.62,0:08:31.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要小心一点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.06,0:08:36.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有那边的框架部分留下一小段比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.86,0:08:37.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样不论是假组
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.66,0:08:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是拆解的时候 都会省不少事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.53,0:08:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.47,0:08:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这部分还不需要特别的技巧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.90,0:08:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做起来应该很开心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.31,0:08:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 好紧张哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.81,0:08:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样会撑不到入墨的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.48,0:08:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那会让人连续紧张到连呼吸都不敢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.72,0:08:59.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的能办得到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.95,0:09:03.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 吉姆的入墨看起来好像更困难说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.22,0:09:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.36,0:09:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来我惨了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.23,0:09:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.20,0:09:13.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…没事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.27,0:09:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们继续吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.00,0:09:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.77,0:09:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高坂呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.54,0:09:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没看到他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.04,0:09:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.84,0:09:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都不会做的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.81,0:09:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 不知不觉就…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.95,0:09:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28}(工程1 打磨)\N(工程2 修边)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.03,0:09:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头部完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.80,0:09:48.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进度不错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.87,0:09:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你动作好快 大野
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.40,0:09:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为吉姆的头部零件比较多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.01,0:09:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.64,0:09:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.01,0:10:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要贴上单眼就完美无缺了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.55,0:10:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.28,0:10:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们挺愉快的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.16,0:10:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓的单眼 功能等于是主要的镜头
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.03,0:10:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你该不会是在顾虑我吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.23,0:10:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯粹是我的自言自语
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.30,0:10:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.54,0:10:27.66,不签,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个游戏无法成立对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.71,0:10:30.94,不签,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果少了第5个人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.18,0:10:35.65,不签,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼故事 其之二
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.71,0:10:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,气氛怎么这么尴尬 别再说了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.75,0:10:39.22,不签,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老实说我不太敢听鬼故事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.28,0:10:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在这让他们觉得很碍事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.92,0:10:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天「不签」的配角们都脱线得挺有意思的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.96,0:10:54.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能因为这样 时乃看起来也比平常要活泼许多
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.27,0:10:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有道理
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.60,0:10:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两…两季长度的好处 就是能看到这…这类额外的题材
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.84,0:11:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.71,0:11:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果只有13话 工作人员光要追上剧情就忙翻了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.64,0:11:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其它呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.71,0:11:09.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小咲 如果你也有看的话 也发表一下意见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.55,0:11:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.62,0:11:15.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.49,0:11:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是稍微拿起来看看而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.66,0:11:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个还处于假组的阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.32,0:11:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…零件很容易散…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.09,0:11:24.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是 马上奉还
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.80,0:11:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真抱歉 玩你的宝贝头部
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.03,0:11:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我才该说对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.71,0:11:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春…春日部她…她也想做吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.61,0:11:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.28,0:11:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会啦 不会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.35,0:11:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.92,0:11:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.22,0:11:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是去邀她看看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.06,0:11:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.82,0:11:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像不太妥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.36,0:11:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她都说没兴趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.59,0:11:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.93,0:12:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做模型明明这么有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.33,0:12:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年夏天我就来挑战One Shoulder好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.97,0:12:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,One Shoulder？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.44,0:12:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露出一边肩膀的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.71,0:12:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 说到One Shoulder
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.61,0:12:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起大野正在做的扎古 我还是比较喜欢扎古
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.55,0:12:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是只有单边有肩甲的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.59,0:12:25.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.82,0:12:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.22,0:12:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来你有什么安排吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.26,0:12:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.60,0:12:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.90,0:12:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 今天还是解散吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.54,0:12:39.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我总觉得好累
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.31,0:12:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.02,0:12:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大野 你在擦指甲油吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.28,0:12:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是新的颜色吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.09,0:12:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.09,0:12:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想应该也不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.10,0:13:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.30,0:13:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.77,0:13:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不介意的话 你要不要也跟我们一起做？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.40,0:13:14.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.31,0:13:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为最近常看你来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.68,0:13:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想说你是不是对塑料模型也有兴趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.45,0:13:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别闹了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.72,0:13:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找别人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.69,0:13:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就跟你说不可能了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.49,0:13:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就继续来打磨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.79,0:13:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个步骤会带来多大的效果 不用我再强调了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.56,0:13:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.60,0:13:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.44,0:13:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 现视研
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.81,0:13:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.21,0:13:55.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还敢问我有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.98,0:13:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的邻居跑来跟我们抗议说溶剂的味道臭死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.12,0:14:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溶剂的味道臭死了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.35,0:14:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.72,0:14:06.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊什么啊 你们该不会…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.86,0:14:08.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为春天到了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.59,0:14:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以会冒出一堆奇怪的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.06,0:14:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你尽管去取缔我们社里的那群笨蛋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.18,0:14:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤脑筋 竟然这时候起风
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.65,0:14:30.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是沾上灰尘就不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.62,0:14:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦沾上根本除不掉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.35,0:14:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有尽量用身体来挡风了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.19,0:14:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在干嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.49,0:14:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有人抗议说社团教室都是溶剂的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.43,0:14:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老实说挺遗憾的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.56,0:14:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要放弃 努力到最后吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.07,0:14:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.14,0:14:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28}(工程3 补土)\N(工程4 入墨)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.92,0:15:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很累吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.52,0:15:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我平常没在运动 所以有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.92,0:15:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就快完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.69,0:15:15.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.20,0:15:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28}(工程5 贴纸)\N(工程6 表面喷漆处理)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.89,0:15:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.49,0:15:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们做得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.26,0:15:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来就剩最后的上漆了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.27,0:15:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.10,0:16:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一步要是失败就救不回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.34,0:16:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以千万别一口气喷太多 要谨慎小心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.04,0:16:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.04,0:16:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从大野先开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.15,0:16:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.05,0:16:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.52,0:16:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要像这样善用手腕的灵巧度
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.39,0:16:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当开始喷与喷完漆时小心别喷到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.99,0:16:21.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.06,0:16:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.59,0:16:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错哦 就是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.96,0:16:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.37,0:16:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为起风让我没办法喷好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.44,0:16:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就趁风停的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.44,0:16:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先放着让它干
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.64,0:16:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后再用砂纸磨过…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.74,0:16:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.05,0:16:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先小心放到地上…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.48,0:16:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.52,0:16:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的吉姆也粘到东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.89,0:16:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦的量产机等会再说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.55,0:16:50.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么这么说 总觉得…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.55,0:16:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什么时候投靠吉恩的？他们超认真的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.72,0:16:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,磨掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.39,0:16:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.09,0:16:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的吉姆…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.43,0:16:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.56,0:16:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现视研
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.00,0:17:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不晓得你们在搞什么鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.36,0:17:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但别把中庭弄脏了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.83,0:17:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.30,0:17:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这什么味道啊 臭死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.54,0:17:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我马上收拾干净哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.44,0:17:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.91,0:17:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你神气成那样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.52,0:17:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在让我看了就烦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.15,0:17:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直呱呱乱叫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.45,0:17:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你啊 我什么时候呱呱乱叫了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.02,0:17:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是刚才啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.42,0:17:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是基于正当的理由 提醒一下那三个人罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.63,0:17:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那点让我看了就烦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.40,0:17:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那点是哪点啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.63,0:17:39.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都已经是春天了 你没别的事好做吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.17,0:17:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不着你多管闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.31,0:17:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大野 你找我有什么事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.22,0:17:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做好了哦 扎古
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.99,0:17:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.42,0:18:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然做得不太好看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.56,0:18:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.63,0:18:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我也不是很懂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.83,0:18:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真了不起 能做到最后
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.77,0:18:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊 对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.97,0:18:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…我可以摸摸看吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.28,0:18:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.22,0:18:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.12,0:18:30.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次不会有问题的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.99,0:18:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要不硬去扭它就不会坏掉对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.66,0:18:37.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.76,0:18:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.30,0:18:49.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关节比我想得还要软啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.61,0:18:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.28,0:18:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是长成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.48,0:18:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动作范围很大嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.52,0:19:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要握住支点再动对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.32,0:19:07.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…尽可能慢慢地…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.69,0:19:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.13,0:19:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.44,0:19:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啪嚓？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.61,0:19:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 脚好像掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.08,0:19:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.31,0:19:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该只是聚乙烯盖掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.92,0:19:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,断掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.75,0:19:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.16,0:19:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故意的 你一定是故意的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.56,0:19:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦 我没有那个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.33,0:19:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你刚才哼了一声
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.13,0:19:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你哼那声是什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.53,0:19:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通常不会那么容易就断的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.24,0:19:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.10,0:19:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.21,0:19:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大野…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.28,0:20:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.38,0:20:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 不要紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.65,0:20:08.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 我一点都…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.95,0:20:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不介意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.46,0:20:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.93,0:20:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪…我怎么…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.96,0:20:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我会赔你的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.93,0:20:20.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次我们一起去买 好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.83,0:20:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了 不用赔啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.60,0:20:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该那么说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.64,0:20:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾 就算你赔了 大野的扎古还是回不来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.11,0:20:37.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那架扎古并不只是买来的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.51,0:20:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是大野花了一个星期 亲自组装完成的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.22,0:20:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大野之所以会流泪 全是因为那一个个步骤的累积
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.66,0:20:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你买来同样的组件 还是抚慰不了她内心的创伤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.93,0:20:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你懂吗？大野的眼泪正是代表了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.43,0:20:59.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塑料模型与用钱买来的玩具之差异
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.41,0:21:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 大野…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.84,0:21:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会 我真的不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.51,0:21:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 为表歉意 我帮你做一件事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.68,0:21:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要我做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.48,0:21:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 你就尽管开口吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.02,0:21:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.52,0:21:22.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你COSPLAY吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.24,0:21:36.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 那个你花多少钱买的？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.14,0:21:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3千円多一点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.68,0:21:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3千円是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.25,0:21:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点钱要我全身都COSPLAY似乎不太划算
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.55,0:21:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一部分就行了吧 一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.75,0:21:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一部分啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.62,0:21:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就那个好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.79,0:21:56.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.19,0:21:57.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.10,0:22:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像比之前的那个更夸张哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.40,0:22:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.10,0:22:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得这个女仆设计要可爱多了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.48,0:22:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你喵～
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.58,0:22:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.49,0:22:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你别想唬我！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.09,0:22:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太赖皮了啦 你明明答应过我的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.01,0:22:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.18,0:24:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春日部的猫耳女仆
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.51,0:24:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚开始一定是很高傲
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.25,0:24:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后慢慢变得顺从
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.68,0:24:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错哦 真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.49,0:24:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(现在正因想像而感到激烈的萌！)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.99,0:24:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些角色当他们焦急时 就会冒出很大的汗滴不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.43,0:24:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说那种汗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.26,0:24:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一看到这种的 整个人都会软掉对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.73,0:24:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有灵机一动或察觉到情况时 头上发出的亮光
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.87,0:24:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有脸颊的微妙色调
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.37,0:24:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸…胸部也有类似情况
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.81,0:24:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表现果然也有流行的趋势啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.98,0:24:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…对了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.94,0:25:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现…现在最让人看不下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.01,0:25:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是分割画面与流行主题曲
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.98,0:25:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.75,0:25:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是那种能在KTV里大喊机器人名字跟招式名称的歌好
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.96,0:25:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,266)}关于特殊封闭环境下说明义务的存在与否

